The Writers' Room, hosted by Academy Award winning writer, Jim Rash,
gets real with the most innovative voices in TV today. This season,

The Good Wife, Sons of Anarchy, Pretty Little Liars and The Walking Dead,
Superman and other Comic Book Adaptations. With shocking revelations and

window into what makes great TV.

Produced by Relativity Television and Sundance Channel.


Host Jim Rash gets a behind-the-scenes look at the groundbreaking
television series "Sons of Anarchy". Creator Kurt Sutter, star
Katey Sagal and Executive Producers Charles Murray and Mike Daniels
reveal the inner workings behind FX's biggest hit.
